    "start_html": "<div id=\"designModeViz\" class=\"appModern clip-content\" data-radium=\"true\" style=\"width: 600px; height: 450px;\"><div class=\"screen\" tabindex=\"1\" data-theme=\"polar\" id=\"login_screen\" style=\"display: block; height: 450px; width: 600px; left: 0px; top: 0px; position: absolute; z-index: 0; background-color: rgb(174, 226, 244); background-size: 600px 450px; background-image: url(&quot;https://levelbuilder-studio.code.org/blockly/media/1x1.gif&quot;);\" data-canonical-image-url=\"\" data-image-type=\"default\"><div contenteditable=\"true\" class=\"textArea\" id=\"text_area3\" style=\"width: 525px; height: 195px; border-style: solid; background-color: rgba(0, 148, 202, 0); color: rgb(14, 14, 14); border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); border-radius: 8px; border-width: 2px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 25px; padding: 5px 15px; position: absolute; left: 55px; top: 145px; margin: 0px;\">Credential Stuffing is an attack where hackers use stolen usernames and passwords from one site to try and log in to other websites, hoping people reused the same login info.</div><img src=\"/level_starter_assets/test-ai-powered-threats-defenses-lesson3-level5/access_granted.png\" data-canonical-image-url=\"image://access_granted.png\" data-image-type=\"file\" data-object-fit=\"contain\" id=\"access_granted\" style=\"height: 95px; width: 455px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-radius: 0px; position: absolute; left: 85px; top: 10px; margin: 0px;\"><img src=\"/level_starter_assets/test-ai-powered-threats-defenses-lesson3-level5/BG2.png\" data-canonical-image-url=\"image://BG2.png\" data-image-type=\"file\" data-object-fit=\"contain\" id=\"bg3\" style=\"height: 115px; width: 600px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-radius: 0px; position: absolute; left: 0px; top: 220px; margin: 0px;\"><img src=\"/level_starter_assets/test-ai-powered-threats-defenses-lesson3-level5/BG1.png\" data-canonical-image-url=\"image://BG1.png\" data-image-type=\"file\" data-object-fit=\"contain\" id=\"bg2\" style=\"height: 115px; width: 600px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-radius: 0px; position: absolute; left: 0px; top: 110px; margin: 0px;\"><img src=\"/level_starter_assets/test-ai-powered-threats-defenses-lesson3-level5/BG3.png\" data-canonical-image-url=\"image://BG3.png\" data-image-type=\"file\" data-object-fit=\"contain\" id=\"bg1\" style=\"height: 115px; width: 600px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-radius: 0px; position: absolute; left: 0px; top: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><input id=\"user_input1\" style=\"margin: 0px; width: 205px; height: 35px; border-style: solid; color: rgb(68, 44, 46); background-color: rgb(172, 207, 222); border-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-radius: 4px; border-width: 1px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; padding: 5px 15px; position: absolute; left: 120px; top: 40px;\" placeholder=\"username\"><img src=\"/level_starter_assets/test-ai-powered-threats-defenses-lesson3-level5/logo1.png\" data-canonical-image-url=\"image://logo1.png\" data-image-type=\"file\" data-object-fit=\"contain\" id=\"logo1\" style=\"height: 80px; width: 110px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-radius: 0px; position: absolute; left: 0px; top: 15px; margin: 0px;\"><input id=\"password_input1\" style=\"margin: 0px; width: 220px; height: 35px; border-style: solid; color: rgb(68, 44, 46); background-color: rgb(172, 207, 222); border-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-radius: 4px; border-width: 1px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; padding: 5px 15px; position: absolute; left: 345px; top: 40px;\" placeholder=\"password\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"textArea\" id=\"text_area1\" style=\"width: 285px; height: 100px; border-style: solid; background-color: rgb(0, 148, 202); color: rgb(239, 250, 255); border-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-radius: 8px; border-width: 2px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; padding: 5px 15px; position: absolute; left: 30px; top: 340px; margin: 0px;\">Enter the credentials below into one of the login portals and press Submit.<div><br></div><div>Username: z_eriK@example.com</div><div>Password: !SecuR3_P@ss#2025</div></div><button id=\"submit_button\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border-style: solid; height: 55px; width: 180px; background-color: rgb(239, 250, 255); color: rgb(0, 148, 202); border-color: rgb(172, 207, 222); border-radius: 28px; border-width: 4px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 23px; position: absolute; left: 355px; top: 340px;\">Submit</button><img src=\"/level_starter_assets/test-ai-powered-threats-defenses-lesson3-level5/logo4.png\" data-canonical-image-url=\"image://logo4.png\" data-image-type=\"file\" data-object-fit=\"contain\" id=\"logo3\" style=\"height: 80px; width: 75px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-radius: 0px; position: absolute; left: 15px; top: 235px; margin: 0px;\"><img src=\"/level_starter_assets/test-ai-powered-threats-defenses-lesson3-level5/logo5.png\" data-canonical-image-url=\"image://logo5.png\" data-image-type=\"file\" data-object-fit=\"contain\" id=\"logo2\" style=\"height: 85px; width: 75px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-radius: 0px; position: absolute; left: 15px; top: 120px; margin: 0px;\"><input id=\"user_input2\" style=\"margin: 0px; width: 205px; height: 35px; border-style: solid; color: rgb(68, 44, 46); background-color: rgb(172, 207, 222); border-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-radius: 4px; border-width: 1px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; padding: 5px 15px; position: absolute; left: 120px; top: 145px;\" placeholder=\"username\"><input id=\"user_input3\" style=\"margin: 0px; width: 205px; height: 35px; border-style: solid; color: rgb(68, 44, 46); background-color: rgb(172, 207, 222); border-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-radius: 4px; border-width: 1px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; padding: 5px 15px; position: absolute; left: 120px; top: 255px;\" placeholder=\"username\"><input id=\"password_input2\" style=\"margin: 0px; width: 220px; height: 35px; border-style: solid; color: rgb(68, 44, 46); background-color: rgb(172, 207, 222); border-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-radius: 4px; border-width: 1px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; padding: 5px 15px; position: absolute; left: 350px; top: 145px;\" placeholder=\"password\"><input id=\"password_input3\" style=\"margin: 0px; width: 220px; height: 35px; border-style: solid; color: rgb(68, 44, 46); background-color: rgb(172, 207, 222); border-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-radius: 4px; border-width: 1px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; padding: 5px 15px; position: absolute; left: 350px; top: 255px;\" placeholder=\"password\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"textArea\" id=\"access_failure\" style=\"width: 235px; height: 60px; border-style: solid; background-color: rgba(0, 148, 202, 0); color: rgb(255, 0, 0); border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); border-radius: 8px; border-width: 2px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; padding: 5px 15px; position: absolute; left: 345px; top: 395px; margin: 0px;\">Username or password was incorrect... try again!</div></div></div>",
    "start_blocks": "  hideElement(\"access_granted\");\n  hideElement(\"access_failure\");\n  hideElement(\"text_area3\");\n\n// Stuffing logic\nonEvent(\"user_input1\", \"input\", function() {\n  var val = getText(\"user_input1\");\n  setText(\"user_input2\", val);\n  setText(\"user_input3\", val);\n});\n\nonEvent(\"user_input2\", \"input\", function() {\n  var val = getText(\"user_input2\");\n  setText(\"user_input1\", val);\n  setText(\"user_input3\", val);\n});\n\nonEvent(\"user_input3\", \"input\", function() {\n  var val = getText(\"user_input3\");\n  setText(\"user_input1\", val);\n  setText(\"user_input2\", val);\n});\n\nonEvent(\"password_input1\", \"input\", function() {\n  var val = getText(\"password_input1\");\n  setText(\"password_input2\", val);\n  setText(\"password_input3\", val);\n});\n\nonEvent(\"password_input2\", \"input\", function() {\n  var val = getText(\"password_input2\");\n  setText(\"password_input1\", val);\n  setText(\"password_input3\", val);\n});\n\nonEvent(\"password_input3\", \"input\", function() {\n  var val = getText(\"password_input3\");\n  setText(\"password_input1\", val);\n  setText(\"password_input2\", val);\n});\n\n// On submit\nonEvent(\"submit_button\", \"click\", function() {\n\n  // Get entered credentials (any input will do since they're synced)\n  var user = getText(\"user_input1\");\n  var pass = getText(\"password_input1\");\n\n  // Replace with your desired values\n  var correctUser = \"z_eriK@example.com\";\n  var correctPass = \"!SecuR3_P@ss#2025\";\n\n  if (user == correctUser && pass == correctPass) {\n    showElement(\"access_granted\");\n    showElement(\"text_area3\");\n    // Hide all elements\n    hideElement(\"user_input1\");\n    hideElement(\"user_input2\");\n    hideElement(\"user_input3\");\n    hideElement(\"password_input1\");\n    hideElement(\"password_input2\");\n    hideElement(\"password_input3\");\n    hideElement(\"submit_button\");\n    hideElement(\"bg1\");\n    hideElement(\"bg2\");\n    hideElement(\"bg3\");\n    hideElement(\"logo1\");\n    hideElement(\"logo2\");\n    hideElement(\"logo3\");    \n    hideElement(\"text_area1\"); \n    hideElement(\"text_area2\"); \n    hideElement(\"access_failure\"); \n  } else {\n    showElement(\"access_failure\");\n  }\n});\n",
    "long_instructions": "## Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Type the `username` and `password` provided into one of the input boxes.\r\n\r\n2. Hit the `Submit` button to gain access to multiple sites at one time by using **credential stuffing**.",
